data.name: label2.Text
data.value: Ratatouille, usually served as a snack, is served with meat dishes or food such as omelets and pancakes. Among the main ingredients of the dish cooked with very little oil in a flat roof and over a high heat; include garlic, onions, tomatoes, zucchini, eggplant, paprika, carrots, thyme, basil and other green herbs. You can be sure that you will like this snack, which you can ask for as a snack.
